A RESOLUTION
1 Applauding Senator Brandon Beach for his exceptional service in the Georgia State Senate,
2 his leadership in both public and private sectors, and congratulating him on his recent
3 appointment as United States Treasurer in the current Trump Administration; and for other
4 purposes.
5 WHEREAS, Senator Brandon Beach has served the people of Georgia with distinction for
6 over two decades, having been elected to the Georgia State Senate in 2013 and currently
7 serving as a Senator representing the 21st District, which includes parts of North Fulton and
8 East Cobb counties; and
9 WHEREAS, Senator Beach has held several influential positions in the Senate, including his
10 service as the Chairman of the Senate Transportation Committee, where he was instrumental
11 in advancing transportation and infrastructure reforms critical to Georgia's economic growth
12 and global competitiveness; and
13 WHEREAS, in addition to his work in transportation, Senator Beach served as Chairman of
14 the Senate Economic Development and Tourism Committee, where he focused on fostering
15 a business-friendly environment in Georgia; his work in this area included attracting major
16 investments in key industries such as technology, entertainment, and manufacturing; and
