39 defined his career in the Georgia State Senate, ensuring that federal fiscal policies serve the
40 best interests of all Americans; and
41 WHEREAS, this prestigious appointment stands as a testament to Senator Beach's tireless
42 dedication to the public good, his leadership in both state and national government, and his
43 ongoing commitment to improving the financial systems that support the country's economy.
44 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
45 honor and applaud Senator Brandon Beach for his exceptional service to the State of
46 Georgia, his remarkable career in both the public and private sectors, and his outstanding
47 contributions to the nation's financial policy as well as congratulate him on his appointment
48 as United States Treasurer in the Trump Administration.
49 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
50 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Senator Brandon
51 Beach.
